import {
  Box,
  Grid,
  InputLabel,
  MenuItem,
  Select,
  TextField,
  Typography,
} from "@mui/material";
import MyButton from "./MyButton";
import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom";
import BaseBox from "./BaseBox";
import DoubleBox from "./DoubleBox";

const OrderListSecond = ({ setPageNumber }) => {
  const navigate = useNavigate();
  return (
    <BaseBox>
      <Box mt={5} width="900px">
        <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight="700">
          1. 운송타입 선택
        </Typography>

        <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight="700">
          2. 화물정보 입력
        </Typography>
        <DoubleBox
          props1={{
            mx: "50px",
            my: "30px",
            py: "15px",
            px: "30px",
            width: "700px",
          }}
          props2={{ p: 2, height: "400px" }}
        >
          <Typography mb={2} fontWeight="700">
            품명
          </Typography>
          <TextField sx={{ mb: 2 }} fullWidth label="상세품명 입력"></TextField>
          <Box mb={2} display="flex" justifyContent="space-between">
            <Box>
              <Typography fontWeight="700">컨테이너 유형</Typography>

              <Select
                sx={{ width: "150px" }}
                labelId="demo-simple-select-label"
                id="demo-simple-select"
                label="유형 선택"
              >
                <MenuItem value={10}>Ten</MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value={20}>Twenty</MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value={30}>Thirty</MenuItem>
              </Select>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Typography fontWeight="700">컨테이너 사이즈</Typography>
              <Select
                sx={{ width: "150px" }}
                labelId="demo-simple-select-label"
                id="demo-simple-select"
                label="유형 선택"
              >
                <MenuItem value={10}>Ten</MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value={20}>Twenty</MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value={30}>Thirty</MenuItem>
              </Select>
            </Box>
            <Box>
              <Typography fontWeight="700">컨테이너 개수</Typography>
              <TextField sx={{ width: "150px" }} label="개수 입력"></TextField>
            </Box>
          </Box>
          <Typography mb={2} fontWeight="700">
            위험물
          </Typography>
          <TextField sx={{ mb: 2 }} fullWidth label="예/아니오"></TextField>
        </DoubleBox>
        <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight="700">
          3. 배송옵션 입력
        </Typography>
        <DoubleBox
          props1={{
            mx: "50px",
            my: "30px",
            py: "15px",
            px: "30px",
            width: "700px",
          }}
          props2={{ p: 2 }}
        >
          <Typography mb={2} fontWeight="700">
            적하보험 가입
          </Typography>
          <TextField sx={{ mb: 2 }} fullWidth label="예/아니오"></TextField>
          <Typography mb={2} fontWeight="700">
            FTA 원산지 증명서 대행발급
          </Typography>
          <TextField sx={{ mb: 2 }} fullWidth label="예/아니오"></TextField>
          <Typography mb={2} fontWeight="700">
            추가사항
          </Typography>
        </DoubleBox>
      </Box>
      <Box width="300px" my={5} display="flex" justifyContent="space-between">
        <MyButton
          type="negative"
          value="뒤로 가기"
          onClick={() => {
            setPageNumber(1);
          }}
          sx={{ width: "100px", height: "50px" }}
        />
        <MyButton
          value="결과 조회"
          onClick={() => {
            navigate("/OrderResult");
          }}
          sx={{ width: "100px", height: "50px" }}
        />
      </Box>
    </BaseBox>
  );
};

export default OrderListSecond;
